snippet: As Hennessy Youngman, the Brooklyn artist Jayson Musson mixes hip-hop slang and profanity with high-minded criticism in a series of YouTube videos.
abstract: Profile of Brooklyn artist Jayson Musson, who critiques art on a series of YouTube videos under the name Hennessy Youngman; like his videos, much of Musson's artwork employs humor to navigate serious issues like politics, race and sex.
lead_paragraph: As Hennessy Youngman, the Brooklyn artist Jayson Musson mixes hip-hop slang and profanity with high-minded criticism in a series of YouTube videos.

headline.seo: Hennessy Youngman Offers Offbeat Art Criticism
